quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,"When that which is coming arrives,"
  56,2,"no one will be able to deny it has come,"
  56,3,"bringing low and raising high."
  56,4,"When the earth is shaken violently"
  56,5,"and the mountains are ground to powder"
  56,6,"and turn to scattered dust,"
  56,7,"then you will be sorted into three classes."
  56,8,"Those on the Right––what people they are!"
  56,9,"Those on the Left––what people they are!"
  56,10,"And those in front––ahead indeed!"